<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قاله ابن أبي حاتم <span class="c2">(العلل ١/ ٢٠٤)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
